Articles.Content:
Is there a list somewhere of names or strings or substrings that you should not be using in your part components or configs?

I came across an issue when naming a door, and the mesh and empty names had the "hatch" substrings everywhere. I managed to deduce that the presence of all the parts with those substrings somewhere lead to the bug where most of the parts, even stock parts, would not show up in the parts menu. changing everything from *hatch* to *somethingelse* fixed it.
